      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% for primary QoI (hemolysis index) on the refined mesh.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed with mesh sizes of 4M, 9M, and 18M cells. GCI for the normalized index of hemolysis was 3.2% between the medium and fine grids. The medium mesh (9M cells) was selected for production runs as the cost-accuracy optimum."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
