      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares the same impeller-volute topology as the subject device. Operating conditions span the intended CPB flow-speed envelope. Fluid properties were matched to diluted blood analogs consistent with CPB priming conditions."
