    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the stated COU. Predicted RH values across all 5 operating points satisfy the RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device.",
